com.fasterxml.jackson.jr.stree

Class JrsValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.jackson.jr.stree.JrsValue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.fasterxml.jackson.core.TreeNode
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    JrsArray, JrsMissing, JrsObject, JrsValue.Scalar

    public abstract class JrsValue
extends Object
implements com.fasterxml.jackson.core.TreeNode
    Shared base class for all "simple" node types of Jackson Jr "simple tree" package; implements TreeNode and is usable via matching TreeCodec implementation (see JacksonJrsTreeCodec).
